staticBinding.value: SELECT DISTINCT S.HOSTNAME,S.CUSTID,S.IP1,S.BAKIP,S.TEMPLATE,S.ISHPMANAGED, S.VLAN1GID,S.TSHIRTSIZE,S.CONTACTEMAIL,M.IOPOOLNAME,S.BAKVLANGID,S.NAT1,CC.HPIO, V.IP as VMMP_IP,S.HASREGBACKUP,S.IP2,S.VLAN2GID, S.VMDATASTORE,CC.VCEM, V.FQDN AS VMMP_FQDN, M.SLALEVEL,CC.CCNAME, (SELECT VMMP_ROOT FROM ( SELECT CLOUD AS VMMP_ROOT,'SCVMM' AS VMMP, SCVMM_ID AS VMMP_ID from SCVMM_CLOUDS UNION SELECT VMDATACENTER AS VMMP_ROOT, 'VCENTER' AS VMMP , VCENTERID AS VMMP_ID FROM VCENTERDCS ) WHERE VMMP_ID = V.ID ) AS VMMP_ROOT , S.ISCVS, S. CSASUBSCRIPTIONID, S.STATUS,VT.ISCLIENTSUPPLIED FROM SERVER S INNER JOIN MOERESPOOL M ON M.RESPOOLID = S.RESPOOLID INNER JOIN CLOUDCELL CC on CC.CCNAME = M.CCNAME LEFT JOIN RESPOOL_VMMP RV ON RV.RESPOOLID = M.RESPOOLID LEFT JOIN VMMP V ON CC.CCNAME = V.CCNAME AND RV.VMMP_TYPE = V.VMMP_TYPE LEFT JOIN VMTEMPLATES VT ON S.TEMPLATE = VT.VMTPLNAME AND S.RESPOOLID = VT.RESPOOLID WHERE CSASVCUUID ='${db.getdetails.csasvcuuid}'

scriptlet.name: default
